  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 2fe0abe2bc63b4548846bb100704dbfe, type: 3}
  m_Name: ManagerIntro
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  dialogue:
  - Boo! Did I scare you?
  - Welcome to Delulu's Donuts! The best donut store in the Dream Realm!
  - You, new employee, are in charge of serving the customers.
  - When greeting a customer, you should be able to ask ONE question. Any more and
    they give this place a 1 star review.
  - 'After a customer is done yapping, press the Donut Button on the left to switch
    views. '
  - Then click on the donut that the customer wants! Make sure you do this after
    you ask your ONE question.
  - Pretty easy, right?
  - For starters, I'll order that super cool purple donut!
  responses:
  - responseText: Anything else I should know?
    dialogueObject: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 4635ee3952037d14ebd25cd51328cfc8, type: 2}
